# Production services (spider.si zone)

Hetzner VPS `46.224.37.205` — SSH `ssh spider.si`, app dir `/opt/spider`.

| Service | URL | Compose | Deploy |
|---------|-----|---------|--------|
| Spider (staging) | https://new.spider.si | `docker-compose.prod.yml` | GitHub Actions on push to `main` |
| Twenty CRM | https://crm.spider.si | `docker-compose.twenty.prod.yml` | `bash deploy/twenty-prod.sh` |
| n8n | https://n8n.spider.si | `docker-compose.n8n.prod.yml` | `bash deploy/n8n-prod.sh` |
| Portainer | https://admin-dash.spider.si | in main compose | with spider stack |

- Caddy in the main stack terminates TLS for all public hostnames (`deploy/Caddyfile`).
- Twenty and n8n join Docker network `spider_default` so Caddy can reach them.
- Env vars live in `/opt/spider/.env` — template: `deploy/env.example`.
- CI copies compose files but does **not** auto-start Twenty/n8n; run the `*-prod.sh` scripts on the VPS.
- n8n ↔ Twenty: use API URL `https://crm.spider.si` (no `/rest`); key from Twenty → Settings → Developers → API & Webhooks. n8n image pre-installs `@linkedpromo/n8n-nodes-twenty`.
- DNS (Cloudflare, gray cloud / DNS-only): A records `crm`, `n8n`, `new`, `admin-dash` → `46.224.37.205`.

Full detail: `AGENTS.md` §9.7 and `deploy/README.md`.
